                            <comment id="11122" author="juergen.hoeller" created="Mon, 27 Sep 2004 00:45:13 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks for spotting this - I&apos;ve changed everything to lower case there. Juergen&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="21500" author="mark warner" created="Fri, 29 Dec 2006 06:57:40 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;how can i get this fix for this?  &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="21502" author="juergen.hoeller" created="Fri, 29 Dec 2006 22:22:04 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Well, this just affected one of our sample applications, JPetStore, and should be fixed there since 1.1.1 (in other words: for ages).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Spring does not deal with table names itself. So it&apos;s always the application&apos;s SQL code that needs to be checked in that respect.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Juergen&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
